test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (1 == 3)
 +  where 1 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x79a7fe352200>([-23])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x79a7fe352200> = [[1, -23], [-23, 1], [1, -23], [-23, 1], [1, -23], [-23]].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 23 == -23
 +  where 23 = <built-in function prod>([-23, -1])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
